Symbol.Script_2D:
pen gs_cont_pen
! Minimal Space unID = 1 hotspot2 0,0, unID : unID=unID+1 call "fa_minimalspace" parameters all MSType = 20, unID = 3000
unID = 10
! Oven Door pen gs_cont_pen fill gs_fill_type poly2_b 5, 1+2+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, b, 1, a, b, 1, a, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, b, -1
hotspot2 0, 0, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 -0.001, 0, unID, A, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A, 0, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 0, 0, unID, B, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0, -0.001, unID, B, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0, B, unID, B, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 A, 0, unID, B, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A, -0.001, unID, B, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A, B, unID, B, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 A/2, 0, unID : unID=unID+1
! Built-in Part if Appl2D AND ApplType_m<>0 then unID = 100 add2 0,b LINE_TYPE ApplLineType
if abs(ApplDepth-b)> EPS then poly2_b 5, 1+2+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0.05,0, 1, 0.05,ApplDepth-b, 1, A-0.05,ApplDepth-b, 1, A-0.05,0, 0, 0.05,0, -1 endif del 1
hotspot2 0.05, 0, unID, ApplDepth, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0.05, -0.001, unID, ApplDepth, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0.05, ApplDepth, unID, ApplDepth, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 A-0.05, 0, unID, ApplDepth, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A-0.05, -0.001, unID, ApplDepth, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 A-0.05, ApplDepth, unID, ApplDepth, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 A/2, ApplDepth/2, unID : unID=unID+1
endif
